13... Nbd7 {[%csl Be4][%cal Be8g6,Ba8e8,Be5d4,Bf6e4] Black is back on track.
At this point, White immediately blundered with} 14. Nf3 $2 {After} exd4 15.
cxd4 Bxe4 $17 {It's clear that White does not have any compensation for the
pawn. Black managed to convert his advantage.} 16. Bg5 Bxd3 17. Qxd3 Qg6 18.
Qb3 Kh8 19. Rae1 Rae8 20. Qa4 Qf5 21. Bxf6 Nxf6 22. Qxa7 Qd7 23. Qb7 Rb8 24.
Qa6 Ra8 25. Qb5 Qxb5 26. cxb5 Rxa2 27. Re7 Rc2 28. Ng5 Ra8 29. Rfe1 h6 30. Ne6
