1. Nf3 Nf6 2. g3 b6 3. Bg2 Bb7 4. O-O e6 5. c4 Be7 6. Nc3 O-O 7. Re1 {[%csl
Be1][%cal Be2e4] This is the most challenging plan. White is planning to
occupy the centre by means of e2-e4.} ({After} 7. d4 Ne4 {, we enter a
